Name: WildStar
About the game: Critically acclaimed and now Free to Play, WildStar is a fantastical sci-fi MMO where you can join your friends or undertake your own epic adventures on the fabled planet Nexus! Explore the huge and amazingly vibrant world packed with unique characters, exotic locations, thrilling challenges and dark mysteries. Recruit fellow citizens of Nexus to solve the primordial puzzles of the universe itself as you experience exhilarating action combat, deep character customization, and one of the most powerful housing systems ever seen in a MMORPG. Key Features: • Free to Play • Fast-paced Action Gameplay • Unique Art Style and Personality • Best-in-Class Housing • Diverse Marketplace Including Hoverboard Mounts, Costumes, Pets, and more • Endless Customization • Amazing Dungeons and Raids with World Bosses Dropping Epic Loot
